(1252, 168, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"ae7e754\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"#FFFDFB\",\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"90f8e52\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ffc8b8d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"La belle histoire de Camina et Amos\",\"header_size\":\"h1\",\"align\":\"center\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Poppins\",\"title_color\":\"#C48249\",\"typography_text_transform\":\"uppercase\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"500\",\"text_stroke_text_stroke_type\":\"yes\",\"text_stroke_text_stroke\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0,\"sizes\":[]},\"text_shadow_text_shadow_type\":\"yes\",\"text_shadow_text_shadow\":{\"horizontal\":0,\"vertical\":0,\"blur\":0,\"color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.3)\"},\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"060\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"015\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"53686a3\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"#FFFDFB\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"121d375\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e71083a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Camina et Amos sont deux alpagas \\u00e0 la fabuleuse histoire qui m\\u00e9rite d\'\\u00eatre racont\\u00e9e. Apr\\u00e8s de multiples p\\u00e9rip\\u00e9ties ils ont aujourd\'hui une place tr\\u00e8s sp\\u00e9ciale aupr\\u00e8s de Jos\\u00e9.<br><\\/p>\\n<p><span class=\\\"need_ref\\\" title=\\\"Ce passage n\\u00e9cessite une r\\u00e9f\\u00e9rence.\\\" style=\\\"cursor:help;\\\"><\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p><span class=\\\"need_ref\\\" title=\\\"Ce passage n\\u00e9cessite une r\\u00e9f\\u00e9rence.\\\" style=\\\"cursor:help;\\\">L\'alpaga est un mammif\\u00e8re domestique de la famille des cam\\u00e9lid\\u00e9s. Alors qu\'on a longtemps consid\\u00e9r\\u00e9 qu\'il \\u00e9tait tr\\u00e8s proche du guanaco, une \\u00e9tude de 2001 a montr\\u00e9 qu\'il avait un anc\\u00eatre commun plus r\\u00e9cent avec la vigogne qu\'avec le guanaco. Comme les autres cam\\u00e9lid\\u00e9s, il rumine mais n\'est pas class\\u00e9 dans la famille des ruminants. Selon le pelage, on distingue deux types d\'alpagas : les suris et les huacayas..<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#524C3F\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Roboto\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":18,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"400\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
